%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20a%20data%20engineer%20returned%20483%25%20trading%20on%20bitcoin's%20value%20inside%20a%20triple%20tax%20benefit%20account%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222504%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Brandon%20Frenchak%20bitcoin%20trader.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a52cbebfebcc4d029e1fb9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221878%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBrandon%20Frenchak%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBrandon%20Frenchak%20leveraged%20health%20savings%20accounts%20for%20tax-free%20bitcoin%20trading%20gains.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20uses%20bitcoin's%20four-year%20cycle%20to%20time%20trades%2C%20focusing%20on%20undervalued%20bitcoin%20trusts.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFrenchak%20achieved%20a%20482.6%25%20gain%20in%202024%20by%20trading%20bitcoin%20trusts%20and%20leveraged%20ETFs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Ffinancial-independence-retire-early%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFinancial%20Independence%2C%20Retire%20Early%3C%2Fa%3E%20(or%20FIRE)%20movement%20was%20Brandon%20Frenchak's%20introduction%20to%20investing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20a%20few%20years%20out%20of%20college%2C%20looking%20for%20ways%20to%20make%20his%20paycheck%20go%20further%2C%20when%20he%20found%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-achieve-financial-independence-advice-from-mr-money-mustache-2019-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMr.%20Money%20Mustache%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20personal%20finance%20blogger%20who%20introduced%20him%20to%20frugality%2C%20saving%20money%2C%20and%20investing%20in%20low-cost%20index%20funds.%20It%20taught%20the%20now%2037-year-old%20data%20engineer%20that%20by%20taking%20the%20right%20steps%20early%2C%20he%20can%20sit%20back%20and%20allow%20his%20investments%20to%20compound%20over%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20like%2C%20'Oh%20man%2C%20this%20is%20going%20to%20take%20forever%2C'%26quot%3B%20Frenchak%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20married%2C%20got%20a%20kid%2C%20and%20then%20I%20had%20another%20one%2C%20and%20now%20I've%20got%20five%20kids.%20So%2C%20I%20was%20like%2C%20'OK%2C%20I%20got%20to%20figure%20out%20a%20way%20to%20accelerate%20this'.%20And%20so%20I%20started%20learning%20about%20value%20investing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20early%20lessons%20in%20personal%20finance%20didn't%20sustain%20his%20interest%2C%20he%20picked%20up%20one%20key%20strategy%3A%20using%20tax-advantaged%20accounts%20that%20could%20further%20compound%20his%20gains%20and%20even%20allow%20him%20to%20keep%20it%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20traders%20who%20use%20a%20brokerage%20account%2C%20Frenchak%20trades%20inside%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-use-health-savings-account-retirement-tool-investing-wealth-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealth%20savings%20account%3C%2Fa%3E%20(HSA).%20It's%20designed%20to%20fund%20medical%20expenses%20and%20has%20three%20tax%20perks%3A%20he%20can%20make%20pre-tax%20contributions%2C%20its%20gains%20are%20not%20subject%20to%20capital%20gains%20or%20dividend%20taxes%2C%20and%20he%20can%20later%20withdraw%20those%20gains%20tax-free%20for%20qualified%20expenses%20or%20without%20penalty%20after%20the%20retirement%20age%20of%2065%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20wife%20just%20had%20a%20baby%2C%20and%20I%20have%20to%20pay%20the%20hospital%2C%20but%20I'll%20wait%20until%20the%20future%20to%20actually%20pull%20it%20out%20and%20pay%20myself%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20Frenchak%20said.%20In%20the%20meantime%2C%20he's%20paying%20the%20medical%20bills%20out%20of%20pocket%2C%20giving%20himself%20more%20time%20to%20trade%20and%20compound%20the%20gains%20inside%20the%20account.%20Since%20an%20HSA%20account%20has%20no%20time%20limit%2C%20he%20can%20withdraw%20the%20funds%20years%20after%20he%20paid%20the%20bill%20and%20still%20qualify%20for%20tax-free%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20a%20traditional%20brokerage%20account%2C%20an%20HSA%20allows%20investment%20in%20multiple%20types%20of%20securities%2C%20including%20stocks%2C%20bonds%2C%20ETFs%2C%20and%20options.%20However%2C%20if%20the%20funds%20are%20withdrawn%20and%20not%20used%20for%20medical%20expenses%20or%20before%20the%20retirement%20age%2C%20a%2020%25%20penalty%20on%20top%20of%20ordinary%20income%20tax%20will%20be%20applied.%20These%20accounts%20may%20also%20have%20daily%20transaction%20limits%20or%20fees%20depending%20on%20the%20provider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22aff15fea-fb19-47c0-bc75-8b4a24ce5f1e%5C%22%3EBecoming%20a%20tax-advantaged%20bitcoin%20trader%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20his%20HSA%20account%2C%20Frenchak%20chose%20to%20trade%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbitcoin-price-target-and-corrections-for-this-bull-run-cmt-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebitcoin-related%3C%2Fa%3E%20securities%20mainly%20because%20he%20understands%20the%20asset's%20four-year%20cycle%2C%20which%20follows%20a%20strong%20three-year%20rally%20followed%20by%20a%20fourth%20year%20where%20it%20plunges.%20He%20has%20observed%20the%20cycle's%20impact%20on%20securities%20tied%20to%20bitcoin.%20Like%20a%20sympathy%20play%2C%20when%20a%20stock%20in%20the%20sector%20begins%20moving%2C%20similar%20securities%20also%20move.%20In%20this%20instance%2C%20bitcoin%20tends%20to%20impact%20bitcoin-mining%20stocks%20and%20ETFs%20or%20trusts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20he%20mainly%20stuck%20with%20trusts%20that%20held%20at%20least%2070%25%20of%20their%20value%20in%20bitcoin.%20He%20did%20not%20trade%20mining%20stocks%20after%20he%20noticed%20that%20their%20shares%20were%20continually%20being%20issued%20and%2C%20as%20a%20result%2C%20diluted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EValuing%20bitcoin%20trusts%20differs%20from%20valuing%20a%20stock%20because%20the%20most%20important%20variables%20are%20bitcoin's%20price%2C%20the%20trust's%20share%20price%2C%20and%20its%20net%20asset%20value%2C%20or%20assets%20less%20liabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20uses%20a%20manual%20spreadsheet%20to%20track%20the%20metrics%20that%20help%20him%20decide%20whether%20a%20trust%20is%20undervalued%20relative%20to%20its%20holdings.%20The%20process%20is%20simple%3A%20it%20considers%20the%20share%20price%20relative%20to%20the%20value%20of%20the%20holdings%20in%20the%20trust%20to%20determine%20the%20premium.%20Those%20with%20the%20highest%20premiums%20are%20the%20positions%20he%20takes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBasically%2C%20you're%20kind%20of%20arbitraging%20what%20the%20difference%20is%20whenever%20the%20market%20is%20being%20irrational%20on%20it%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20pretty%20simple%20metric%2C%26quot%3B%20Frenchak%20said.%20It%20also%20helps%20you%20avoid%20it%20when%20it's%20irrationally%20overpriced%2C%20like%20the%202021%20bull%20market%20when%20Grayscale%20Digital%20Large%20Cap%20Fund%20(GDLC)%20traded%20at%2050%25%20over%20its%20net%20asset%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22GDLC%20NAV%20chart.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a676947bb3f854015c3fe9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221212%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGrayscale%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20traded%20bitcoin%20trusts%20during%20the%202021%20US%20Investing%20Championship%2C%20an%20annual%20contest%20for%20retail%20traders%20run%20by%20former%20math%20professor%20Norman%20Zadeh.%20But%20he%20was%20in%20losing%20territory%20because%20he%20had%20not%20paid%20close%20attention%20to%20the%20NAV%20and%20took%20up%20a%20position%20in%20the%20Grayscale%20Digital%20Large%20Cap%20Fund%20(GDLC)%20when%20its%20share%20price%20was%20on%20par%20with%20and%20sometimes%20above%20its%20holdings%2C%20assuming%20the%20bull%20market%20would%20continue%20to%20push%20its%20price%20higher.%20But%20he%20ended%20up%20riding%20the%20position%20down%20and%20taking%20a%20loss%2C%20losing%20almost%20the%20full%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20he%20re-entered%20the%20competition%2C%20finishing%20with%20a%20482.6%25%20gain%2C%20according%20to%20the%20competition's%20founder%20and%20documents%20viewed%20by%20Business%20Insider%20for%20the%20enhanced%20growth%20division%2C%20which%20allows%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Ffutures-investing%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrading%20of%20futures%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhat-is-options-trading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoptions%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20example%20of%20one%20of%20his%20successful%20trades%20was%20a%20swap%20he%20made%20between%20two%20BTC%20trusts.%20In%20mid-January%2C%20Frenchak%20saw%20that%20the%20Bitwise%2010%20Crypto%20Index%20Fund's%20(BITW)%20market%20price%20had%20dropped%20substantially%20to%20nearly%20%2415%20a%20share%20while%20its%20NAV%20was%20around%20%2435.%20Meanwhile%2C%20GDLC%20was%20also%20trading%20near%20%2415%2C%20but%20its%20NAV%20was%20%2424.%20He%20sold%20his%20full%20position%20in%20GDLC%20and%20moved%20to%20BITW%2C%20entering%20at%20around%20%2415%20a%20share%20and%20selling%20at%20%2421.50%20over%20the%20span%20of%20a%20few%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20went%20100%25%20in%20because%20it%20was%20the%20most%20undervalued%20at%20that%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20Frenchak%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20big%20part%20of%20his%20winnings%20came%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrostrategy-bitcoin-100000-michael-saylor-crypto-markets-investing-strategy-analysis-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMicrostrategy%3C%2Fa%3E%20(MSTR)%2C%20though%20not%20because%20its%20net%20asset%20value%20was%20higher%20than%20its%20share%20price.%20MSTR's%20price%20had%20a%20history%20of%20surpassing%20its%20NAV%20by%20more%20than%20five%20times%20in%20the%20previous%20crypto%20bull%20market%20from%202020%20to%202021.%20Based%20on%20that%20historical%20precedent%2C%20he%20figured%20that%20MSTR's%20stock%20price%20could%20again%20trade%20at%20a%20significant%20premium%20to%20its%20NAV.%20He%20was%20right%3A%20last%20year%2C%20MSTR%20traded%20at%20up%20to%20a%20200%25%20premium%20to%20its%20NAV.%20The%20company%20(now%20called%20Strategy)%20saw%20its%20stock%20soar%20359%25%20in%202024%20as%20it%20aggressively%20added%20to%20its%20reserves%20of%20bitcoin%2C%20which%20itself%20more%20than%20doubled%20in%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrenchak%20also%20traded%20options%20and%2C%20eventually%2C%20leveraged%20ETFs%20designed%20to%20multiply%20gains%20or%20losses%20in%20stocks.%20He%20began%20by%20buying%20at-the-money%20calls%20on%20MSTR%20and%20was%20successful%20early%20in%20the%20year%2C%20but%20lost%20money%20when%20he%20exited%20too%20soon%20in%20the%20second%20attempt.%20He%20then%20moved%20on%20to%20two%20leveraged%20products%3A%20the%20Defiance%20Daily%20Target%202x%20Long%20MSTR%20ETF%20(MSTX)%20and%20T-Rex%202X%20Long%20MSTR%20Daily%20Target%20ETF%20(MSTU).%20Both%20multiplied%20what%20he%20would%20have%20gained%20by%20only%20owning%20MSTR%20stock%20%E2%80%94%20but%20they%20would%20have%20amplified%20his%20losses%20if%20the%20stock%20went%20south.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-trade-bitcoin-triple-tax-benefit-account-hsa-trader-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739008501000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a52ce27bb3f854015c18ac%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-trade-bitcoin-triple-tax-benefit-account-hsa-trader-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22He%20returned%20483%25%20trading%20on%20the%20gap%20between%20a%20stock's%20net%20asset%20value%20and%20share%20price%20using%20a%20tax-free%20acco