e%20gets%20to%20tell%20that%20story%2C%20gets%20to%20leverage%20that%20story.%20It%20becomes%20not%20only%20a%20talking%20point%2C%20but%20a%20source%20of%20connections%2C%20a%20source%20of%20storytelling%2C%20a%20source%20of%20business%20opportunities%2C%20and%20more.%20Even%20if%20that's%20not%20your%20main%20purpose%2C%20it's%20an%20ancillary%20benefit%20that%20can't%20be%20ignored%20and%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20promote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2216e03bc1-53ed-4db5-bd54-4d07a7a082bb%5C%22%3EJordan%20put%20his%20own%20stamp%20on%20the%20mansion%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20of%20the%20homes%20we%20deal%20with%20are%20one-of-one%20custom%20builds%20built%20specifically%20for%20the%20client.%20We%20use%20the%20typical%20%26quot%3Bcomp%26quot%3B%20analysis%20when%20we're%20running%20numbers%20to%20get%20a%20baseline%2C%20and%20then%20we%20adjust%20up%20or%20down%20based%20on%20different%20attributes%20of%20the%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20way%20to%20capture%20the%20true%20value%20of%20Michael%20Jordan's%20estate%20based%20on%20comparable%20properties.%20The%20best%20houses%20in%20the%20neighborhood%20are%20maybe%2010%2C000%20square%20feet.%20This%20one%20is%2056%2C000%20square%20feet%20%E2%80%94%20there's%20no%20real%20comp%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20he%20was%20such%20a%20huge%20public%20figure%2C%20he%20wanted%20to%20be%20able%20to%20enjoy%20himself%20in%20his%20own%20home%20without%20having%20to%20face%20paparazzi%20and%20hang%20out%20with%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou've%20earned%20the%20right%20to%20customize%20the%20hell%20out%20of%20the%20house%2C%20so%20make%20it%20your%20own%20and%20enjoy%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJordan%20had%20a%2023%20on%20the%20gate.%20The%20house%20has%20its%20own%20full-court%20gym%2C%20full%20training%20facilities%2C%20cigar%20lounges%2C%20and%20a%20swimming%20pool%20shaped%20like%20a%20basketball%20hoop.%20It%20has%20its%20own%20pond%20stocked%20with%20fish.%20It%20has%20a%20par-three%20golf%20hole.%20It%20has%20a%20whole%20hair%20salon%20for%20his%20wife.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20front%20gate%20outside%20Michael%20Jordan's%20Chicago%20mansion.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6647875814fb5b23cc5ddc91%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20front%20gate%20outside%20Michael%20Jordan's%20former%20Chicago%20mansion.%3Cp%3EScott%20Olson%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EYou're%20doing%20yourself%20a%20disservice%20by%20trying%20to%20normalize%20those%20things.%20If%20anything%2C%20you%20have%20to%20lean%20into%20those%20differentiators%20%E2%80%94%20capture%20that%20story%20and%20tell%20it%20the%20right%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bd3fea2d-4a39-4123-a8dc-e0b7bd612664%5C%22%3EI%20wanted%20to%20raise%20the%20house's%20profile%20in%20the%20hopes%20of%20landing%20a%20buyer%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20call%20to%20get%20the%20listing%20wasn't%20surreal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20call%20that%20was%20surreal%20was%20when%20Michael%20Jordan%20himself%20called%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20called%20me%20to%20tell%20me%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20about%20the%20vision%20and%20answer%20a%20few%20questions%20I%20had%20to%20extract%20the%20story%20behind%20building%20such%20an%20amazing%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20not%20just%20selling%20another%20house%2C%20not%20just%20selling%20a%20bigger%2C%20better%20property%20in%20the%20neighborhood.%20The%20idea%20of%20selling%20a%20legendary%20estate%2C%20a%20trophy%20property%2C%20hadn't%20fully%20been%20embraced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wanted%20to%20begin%20repositioning%20the%20marketing%20strategy%20by%20changing%20the%20price.%20I%20picked%20numbers%20that%20added%20up%20to%20the%20number%2023%3A%20%2414%2C855%2C000.%20That%20became%20international%20news%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20offered%20prospective%20buyers%20a%20pair%20of%20each%20Jordan%20shoe%20that%20had%20come%20out%20in%20the%20buyer's%20size%20if%20they%20bought%20the%20home.%20That%20made%20international%20news.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22michael%20jordan%20shoes%20air%20jordan%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5ebf000f4dca681d971a46e8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJordan%20launching%20a%20line%20of%20Air%20Jordans.%3Cp%3EKelly%20Kline%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pricing%20strategy%20was%20more%20than%20fair.%20It%20was%20just%20a%20matter%20of%20capturing%20the%20right%20story%20to%20bring%20in%20the%20right%20buyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would%20get%20calls%20directly%20from%20qualified%20buyers%20asking%20about%20it.%20I%20would%20also%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20silly%20and%20fun%20calls%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20can%20I%20play%20Michael%20one-on-one%20for%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20house%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20some%20markets%20and%20some%20properties%20that%20take%20two%20or%20three%20years%20to%20sell.%20It's%20not%20very%20common%2C%20but%20some%20do%20take%20more%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2281401c3d-be81-46b5-804c-f6a3e829f273%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20didn't%20get%20a%20chance%20to%20close%20the%20deal%2C%20but%20I%20think%20I%20could%20have%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20only%20had%20the%20listing%20for%2011%20months%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20changed%20companies%20and%20the%20listing%20stayed%20with%20the%20old%20company%20%E2%80%94%20and%20then%20that%20company%20lost%20the%20listing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20given%20a%20little%20bit%20longer%2C%20we%20would've%20been%20able%20to%20get%20the%20deal%20done.%20Given%20the%20initial%20momentum%20and%20increase%20in%20visibility%20%E2%80%94%20the%20increase%20in%20excitement%20and%20showings%20%E2%80%94%20I%20think%20we%20would%20have%20been%20able%20to%20get%20more%20than%20%249.5%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20the%20number%20that%20it%20sells%20for%20is%20the%20number%20that%20everyone%20agrees%20to.%20That's%20what%20a%20buyer%20decided%20they%20were%20willing%20to%20pay%2C%20and%20what%20Michael%20Jordan%20was%20willing%20to%20sell%20it%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20also%20think%20that%20there%20are%20some%20things%20that%20can%20always%20be%20done%20differently%20to%20squeeze%20a%20bit%20more%20value%20out%20of%20a%20property%20like%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcelebrity-real-estate-agent-tried-to-sell-michael-jordan-mansion-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739007782000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a6645f6630eb10385bf701%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcelebrity-real-estate-agent-tried-to-sell-michael-jordan-mansion-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kofi%20Nartey%20used%20creative%20ways%20to%20lure%20a%20buyer%20for%20Michael%20Jordan's%20huge%20estate%20in%20the%20Chicago%20suburbs%2C%20which%20sat%20on%20the%20market%20for%2012%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jpandy%40insider.com%20(Jordan%20Pandy)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcelebrity-real-estate-agent-tried-to-sell-michael-jordan-mansion-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20Manish%20Sisodia%20Among%205%20AAP%20Heavyweights%20Who%20Lost%20In%20Delhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20BJP%20scored%20a%20massive%20win%20in%20Delhi%2C%20improving%20its%20tally%20by%20nearly%2040%20seats%2C%20five%20key%20leaders%20of%20the%20ruling%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20suffered%20a%20crushing%20defeat.%20These%20include%20AAP's%20national%20convener%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20the%20party's%20Number%202%20Manish%20Sisodia%20and%20prominent%20minister%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%20AAP's%20key%20leaders%20who%20lost%20out%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArvind%20Kejriwal%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20national%20convener%20of%20the%20AAP%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20entered%20politics%20with%20a%20message%20of%20change%20after%20the%20anti-corruption%20movement%20against%20the%20UPA%20government.%20First%20sworn%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20for%20a%20short%20duration%20in%202013%2C%20he%20led%20AAP%20to%20thumping%20victories%20in%20the%202015%20and%202020%20elections.%20He%20was%20arrested%20last%20year%20in%20a%20corruption%20case%20linked%20to%20Delhi's%20now-scrapped%20liquor%20policy.%20On%20being%20granted%20bail%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20quit%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20said%20he%20would%20return%20to%20the%20post%20only%20after%20the%20%26quot%3Bpeople's%20court%26quot%3B%20gave%20a%20verdict%20in%20his%20favour.%20He%20lost%20to%20BJP's%20Parvesh%20Verma%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EManish%20Sisodia%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Delhi's%20former%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20the%20Number%202%20leader%20in%20AAP%2C%20Mr%20Sisodia%20has%20lost%20to%20BJP's%20Tarvinder%20Singh%20Marwah%20in%20Jangpura.%20A%20three-time%20MLA%20from%20east%20Delhi's%20Patparganj%2C%20he%20had%20switched%20to%20Jangpura%20for%20this%20election.%20Mr%20Sisodia%20was%20arrested%20in%20a%20corruption%20case%20linked%20to%20the%20liquor%20policy%20in%202023%20and%20spent%20nearly%20one-and-a-half%20years%20in%20jail%20before%20he%20got%20bail.%20Like%20Mr%20Kejriwal%2C%20he%20too%20had%20refused%20to%20take%20up%20a%20seat%20in%20the%20government%20before%20the%20%26quot%3Bpeople's%20verdict%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESaurabh%20Bharadwaj%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20prominent%20AAP%20leader%2C%20Mr%20Bhardwaj%20won%20the%20Greater%20Kailash%20seat%20thrice%20in%202013%2C%20but%20lost%20out%20to%20BJP's%20Shikha%20Roy%20this%20time.%20A%20minister%20