5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etank%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20airplane%20%E2%80%94%20to%20devise%20its%20blitzkrieg%20strategy%20in%20World%20War%20II%2C%20while%20America's%20failure%20in%20Vietnam%20spurred%20military%20reforms%20that%20bore%20fruit%20in%20Desert%20Storm.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERussia's%20record%20on%20military%20reform%20is%20checkered.%20Defeat%20in%20World%20War%20I%20generated%20innovations%20in%20mechanized%20warfare%20by%20Soviet%20theorists%20like%20General%20Mikhail%20Tukhachevsky%20in%20the%201930s.%20Poor%20combat%20performance%20in%20Chechnya%20in%20the%201990s%2C%20and%20Georgia%20in%202008%2C%20led%20to%20calls%20for%20changes%2C%20such%20as%20shifting%20away%20from%20mass%20conscript%20armies%20to%20a%20professional%20volunteer%20force.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20problem%20is%20that%20these%20reforms%20have%20tended%20to%20be%20stymied%20by%20obstacles%20such%20as%20Russia's%20economic%20woes%20after%20the%20collapse%20of%20the%20Soviet%20Union%2C%20reactionary%20Soviet-era%20generals%20resistant%20to%20change%2C%20cronyism%20and%20politicians%20distrustful%20of%20their%20own%20military%3B%20Tukhachevsky%20was%20executed%20by%20Stalin%20in%201938.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERAND%20expects%20Russia%20will%20ultimately%20choose%20some%20mixture%20of%20the%20various%20reform%20options.%20The%20final%20decision%20will%20be%20shaped%20by%20several%20factors%2C%20including%20how%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20ends%2C%20the%20strength%20of%20Russia's%20economy%2C%20declining%20birthrates%2C%20the%20ability%20to%20develop%20and%20manufacture%20advanced%20military%20technologies%2C%20the%20opportunity%20to%20import%20technologies%20that%20can't%20be%20produced%20domestically%2C%20and%20relations%20with%20allies%20such%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-plan-divide-china-russia-axis-is-likely-fail-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3C