20and%20it%20could%20be%20primed%20to%20do%20so%20again.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20much%20longer%20can%20the%20Magnificent%20Seven%20stocks%20continue%20to%20dominate%20the%20equity%20market%3F%20History%20suggests%20their%20era%20of%20outperformance%20is%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20fading.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20analysis%20by%20Glenmede%20Investment%20Management%2C%20concentration%20levels%20in%20the%20top%2010%25%20of%20US%20stocks%20now%20rival%20levels%20seen%20in%201929%20and%201999%2C%20the%20peaks%20of%20the%20two%20most%20notorious%20market%20bubbles%20in%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20trouble%20ahead%20for%20the%20largest%20stocks%20in%20the%20market%20%E2%80%94%20and%20by%20default%2C%20the%20cap-weighted%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20index%20%E2%80%94%20warns%20Alex%20Atanasiu%2C%20a%20portfolio%20manager%20at%20the%20firm%2C%20which%20oversees%20%246.6%20billion%20in%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20now%2C%20the%20average%20market%20cap%20of%20the%20top%2010%25%20of%20US%20stocks%20relative%20to%20that%20of%20the%20average%20stock%20between%20the%2030th%20and%2070th%20percentiles%20is%20three%20standard%20deviations%20above%20normal%20levels%20as%20investors%20pile%20into%20AI-related%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22market%20concentration%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a6712ceb4be2fff9a3fed8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221352%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGlenmede%20Investment%20Management%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20both%20instances%20where%20this%20happened%2C%20the%20top%2010%25%20of%20stocks%20delivered%20negative%20returns%20over%20the%20following%20three-%20and%20five-year%20periods.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20average%20stock%20between%20the%2030th%20and%2070th%20percentiles%20returned%2050%25%20and%2069%25%20over%20those%20timeframes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221766%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22forward%20stock%20market%20returns%20after%20high%20concentration%20levels%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a671646630eb10385bfa90%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221584%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGlenmede%20Investment%20Management%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20tale%20of%20two%20markets%2C%26quot%3B%20Atanasiu%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20saying%20they're%20going%20to%20crash%20tomorrow%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued%2C%20referencing%20the%20top%20decile%20of%20stocks%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20you%20tend%20to%20get%20them%20either%20crashing%20and%20coming%20back%20or%20just%20not%20gaining%20much%2C%20but%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20market%20tends%20to%20be%20just%20fine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20way%20of%20looking%20at%20how%20concentrated%20the%20market%20has%20become%20at%20the%20top%20is%20to%20compare%20the%20performance%20of%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20cap-weighted%20index%20against%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20equal-weight%20index.%20All%20of%20the%20constituents%20in%20the%20latter%20affect%20the%20index's%20performance%20equally%2C%20so%20it%20can%20act%20as%20a%20better%20gauge%20of%20how%20the%20broader%20market%20is%20behaving%20outside%20of%20the%20top%20names.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20historically%20elevated%20returns%20from%20the%20Magnificent%20Seven%20stocks%2C%20the%20cap-weighted%20index%20has%20drastically%20outperformed%20the%20equal-weight%20index.%20The%20equal-weight%20index%20is%2037%25%20below%20its%20relative%20performance%20trend%20to%20the%20cap-weighted%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%2C%20Atanasiu%20said%2C%20slightly%20more%20than%201999%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%201999%20lows%2C%20the%20equal-weight%20index%20went%20on%20a%20fierce%20five-year%20rally%2C%20Atanasiu%20said%2C%20outperforming%20the%20cap-weighted%20index%20by%20more%20than%2010%25%20per%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221714%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22S%26amp%3BP%20500%20equal%20weight%20vs%20cap-weighted%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a671946630eb10385bfa98%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221340%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGlenmede%20Investment%20Management%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAtanasiu's%20outlook%20for%20relatively%20poor%20returns%20ahead%20is%20in%20line%20with%20some%20major%20Wall%20Street%20names.%20Goldman%20Sachs'%20chief%20US%20equity%20strategist%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsp500-outlook-next-decade-forecast-david-kostin-goldman-stocks-strategist-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDavid%20Kostin%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20last%20year%20that%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20would%20return%203%25%20annually%20through%202034%2C%20given%20where%20the%20Shiller%20CAPE%20ratio%20sits.%20Morgan%20Stanley's%20chief%20investment%20officer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsp500-returns-outlook-decade-flat-returns-mike-wilson-morgan-stanley-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMike%20Wilson%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20returns%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bflat-ish%26quot%3B%20over%20that%20time.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhere-to-invest-now-long-term-rob-arnott-research-affiliates-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERob%20Arnott%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Research%20Affiliates%2C%20also%20recently%20told%20BI%20that%20he%20expects%20large-cap%20stocks%20to%20enter%20a%20bear%20market%20while%20value%20stocks%20outperform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20fascinating%20to%20note%20that%2C%20from%20March%202000%20to%20March%202002%2C%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20was%20down%2027%25%2C%20while%20Russell%202000%20Value%20was%20up%2053%25%20(Russell%201000%20Value%20and%20the%20full%20Russell%202000%20were%20both%20flat%2C%20shrugging%20off%20a%20nasty%20bear%20market)%3B%20then%20everything%20fell%20about%2025%25%20through%20end-September%2C%26quot%3B%20Arnott%20told%20BI%20in%20November.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20valuation%20gaps%20get%20wide%20enough%2C%20markets%20can%20utterly%20disconnect.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20weeks%2C%20investors%20may%20have%20gotten%20a%20glimpse%20at%20what%20such%20a%20situation%20could%20look%20like%20amid%20the%20DeepSeek%20R1%20chatbot%20announcement.%20The%20AI%20chatbot%2C%20which%20is%20cheaper%20to%20build%20and%20run%20than%20ChatGPT%20models%2C%20sent%20tech%20stocks%20tumbling%20in%20late%20January.%20Meanwhile%2C%20value%20factors%20like%20the%20Vanguard%20Value%20Index%20Fund%20ETF%20(VTV)%20remained%20mostly%20flat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20never%20had%20any%20price%20pressures%20on%20AI.%20It's%20just%20whatever%20I%20can%20spend%20to%20try%20to%20get%20that%20first-mover%20advantage.%20And%20now%20you're%20seeing%20some%20cost%20pressures%2C%26quot%3B%20Atanasiu%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20you're%20going%20to%20come%20to%20grips%20with%20people's%20projections%20for%20seismic%20earnings%20growth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-why-sp500-due-for-dismal-returns-glenmede-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739005201000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a667e6eb4be2fff9a3fc54%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-why-sp500-due-for-dismal-returns-glenmede-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22How%20much%20longer%20can%20the%20Magnificent%20Seven%20stocks%20continue%20to%20dominate%3F%20History%20suggests%20not%20long.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22wedwards%40businessinsider.com%20(William%20Edwards)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-why-sp500-due-for-dismal-returns-glenmede-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20AAP%20Crash%3A%20Is%20This%20A%20Setback%20Or%20A%20Wipeout%3F%20Only%20Kejriwal%20Can%20Decide%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMany%20may%20be%20tempted%20to%20write%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party's%20(AAP)%20obituary%20today%2C%20but%20that%20may%20be%20both%20hasty%20and%20tragic.%20The%20AAP's%20defeat%20in%20Delhi%20is%20basically%20a%20journey%20from%20Dreamland%20to%20Crashland.%20Much%20before%20the%20results%20were%20out%2C%20I%20had%20argued%20that%20this%20was%20the%20most%20opportune%20time%20for%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20to%20win%20the%20election.%20The%20results%20of%20the%20Delhi%20assembly%20elections%20are%20shocking%20for%20both%20AAP%20and%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20but%20it's%20they%20who%20must%20take%20the%20blame%20for%20the%20rout%2C%20and%20gracefully%20accept%20their%20mistakes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKejriwal%20had%20emerged%20on%20the%20national%20scene%20as%20a%20radical%20revolutionary%20who%20promised%20to%20change%20the%20politics%20of%20the%20country.%20Instead%2C%20it%20was%20politics%20that%20changed%20Kejriwal.%20Twelve%20years%20in%20power%20had%20turned%20him%20into%20yet%20another%20politician%20who%20lost%20all%20his%20moral%20lustre%20and%20charisma.%20Nothing%20could%20be%20more%20tragic%20than%20the%20defeat%20of%20Kejriwal%20from%20his%20own%20seat%2C%20the%20New%20Delhi%20constituency.%20It's%20a%20lesson%20for%20all%20politicians%20who%20think%20they%20are%20bigger%20than%20the%20party%20and%20the%20collective%20wisdom%20of%20the%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20things%20went%20against%20the%20AAP%20in%20this%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Same%20Old%2C%20Same%20Old%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20the%20AAP's%20biggest%20undoing%20was%20that%20it%20was%20no%20longer%20seen%20as%20a%20party%20with%20a%20difference.%20Moral%20capital%20used%20to%20be%20its%20unique%20asset%2C%20something%20that%20few%20parties%20in%20contemporary%20politics%20could%20claim.%20But%20over%20time%2C%20the%20AAP%20sacrificed%20its%20core%20values%3B%20it%20became%20vulnerable%20as%20its%20most%20loyal%20supporters%20lost%20support%20in%20both%20the%20party%20and%20its%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20similar%20thing%20had%20happened%20with%20the%20BJP%20in%201984%2C%20when%20it%20could%20win%20only%20two%20seats%20in%20the%20national%20election.%20Yes%2C%20Indira%20Gandhi's%20assassination%20was%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20for%20the%20BJP's%20dismal%20performance%2C%20but%20it%20was%20also%20a%20fact%20that%20the%20BJP%20had%20abandoned%20its%20core%20ideological%20value%20of%20Hindutva%20and%20had%20been%20trying%20to%20be%20secular.%20True%2C%20the%20AAP%20is%20not%20an%20ideological%20party%2C%20but%20it%20had%20a%20certain%20moral%20virtue%20and%20responsibility.%20It%20was%20this%20moral%20image%20that%20had%20helped%20it%20win%20landslide%20mandates%20in%20both%202015%20and%202020%20assembly%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Losing%20The%20Moral%20Edge%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20serious%20corruption%20charges%20dented%20Kejriwal's%20image.%20The%20alleged%20liquor%20scam%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20an%20Albatross%20around%20his%20neck.%20It%20landed%20him%20in%20jail%2C%20along%20with%20his%20colleagues%20Manish%20Sisodia%2C%20Sanjay%20Singh%20and%20others.%20However%2C%20it%20was%20the%20%E2%80%98Sheesh%20Mahal'%20controversy%20that%20proved%20to%20be%20the%20final%20straw.%20The%20voters%20could%20not%20believe%20that%20a%20leader%20who%20criticised%20every%20politician%20for%20their%20wealth%20and%20fancy%20bungalows%20had%20ironically%20built%20a%20plush%20house%20for%20himself%20worth%20crores.%20The%20leaked%20images%20of%20his%20renovated%20house%20did%20more%20damage%20to%20Kejriwal's%20personal%20image%20than%20the%20liquor%20scam.%20He%20did%20realise%20this%2C%20and%20attempted%20some%20damage%20control%20by%20resigning%20from%20office%20and%20leaving%20the%20chief%20minister's%20bungalow%20for%20a%20much%20more%20modest%20accommodation.%20But%20the%20deed%20was%20done.%20The%20middle%20class%2C%20which%20had%20been%20the%20biggest%20pillar%20of%20the%20AAP%20saga%20in%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20had%20already%20been%20disillusioned%2C%20and%20ended%20up%20deserting%20the%20AAP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20The%20Policy%20Paralysis%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThirdly%2C%20the%20non-performance%20of%20the%20AAP%20government%20in%20its%20third%20term%20from%202020%20to%202025%20contributed%20to%20its%20rout.%20In%20its%20first%20full%20term%2C%20the%20AAP%20government%20was%20seen%20to%20be%20delivering%20on%20its%20promises.%20Other%20than%20the%20provision%20of%20free%20electricity%20and%20water%2C%20schools%20in%20Delhi%20were%20turned%20into%20better%20centres%20for%20education%2C%20a%20step%20that%20brought%20global%20appreciation%20for%20the%20government.%20The%20introduction%20of%20Mohalla%20clinics%20was%20also%20an%20excellent%20step%20to%20improve%20primary%20healthcare.%20It%20became%20a%20huge%20hit%20among%20large%20sections%20of%20society%20that%20could%20not%20afford%20costly%20medical%20care%20at%20private%20facilities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20term%2C%20however%2C%20the%20AAP%20government%20suffered%20from%20policy%20and%20administrative%20paralysis.%20It%20was%20seen%20as%20constantly%20wrangling%20with%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20for%20power.%20The%20tussle%20between%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20AAP%20government%20brought%20governance%20in%20the%20city%20to%20a%20standstill.%20Broken%20roads%20and%20open%20sewer%20lines%20were%20for%20everyone%20to%20see.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3E4.%20When%20Theatrics%20Don't%20Pay%20Off%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFourthly%2C%2010%20years%20is%20a%20long%20time%20for%20anti-incumbency%20to%20set%20in%20against%20any%20government.%20Even%20the%20Modi%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%20could%20not%20avoid%20the%20repercussions%20of%20anti-incumbency%20in%20the%202024%20parliamentary%20elections.%20Despite%20the%20party's%20expectations%20that%20it%20would%20get%20more%20than%20400%20seats%20along%20with%20its%20allies%2C%20it%20could%20not%20get%20a%20majority%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20and%20had%20to%20rely%20on%20smaller%20parties%20to%20form%20a%20government.%20The%20AAP%20government%20was%20no%20exception.%20Its%20failure%20was%20that%20instead%20of%20trying%20to%20arrest%20and%20address%20the%20disillusionment%20of%20its%20voters%2C%20it%20indulged%20in%20theatrics.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Volunteers%20Were%20Tired%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20in%20previous%20elections%2C%20the%20AAP's%20biggest%20asset%20was%20its%20selfless%20volunteer%20force.%20However%2C%20through%20these%20years%2C%20it%20did%20not%20pay%20attention%20to%20creating%20a%20party%20structure%20across%20the%20national%20capital.%20In%20contrast%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20always%20had%20the%20advantage%20of%20having%20a%20robust%20organisation.%20Kejriwal%2C%20by%20nature%2C%20does%20not%20believe%20in%20that.%20In%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20many%20volunteers%20felt%20ignored%20and%20exploited.%20Slowly%20but%20steadily%2C%20they%20were%20disheartened%20and%20disillusioned.%20Most%20of%20them%20either%20left%20the%20party%20and%20went%20back%20to%20their%20usual%20lives%2C%20or%2C%20they%20joined%20other%20parties.%20In%20this%20election%2C%20the%20AAP%20had%20to%20rely%20on%20paid%20workers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20it%20might%20be%20too%20early%20to%20be%20writing%20an%20obituary%20for%20the%20AAP.%20The%20AAP%20has%20lost%20almost%2010%25%20votes%20compared%20to%20its%20tally%20in%20the%202020%20assembly%20elections.%20But%20it%20still%20commands%20almost%2043%25%20votes.%20It%20still%20controls%20the%20capital's%20municipal%20body.%20In%20Punjab%2C%20it%20has%20a%20government%20with