elhi%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnti-Incumbency%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAAP%20scored%20big%20victories%20in%20Delhi%20in%20the%202015%20and%202020%20polls.%20And%20its%20first%20two%20terms%20saw%20impressive%20work%20in%20sectors%20such%20as%20health%20and%20education.%20Power%20and%20water%20subsidies%20kept%20voters%20happy%20and%20the%20BJP%2C%20despite%20sweeping%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20in%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20struggled%20to%20gain%20ground%20during%20Assembly%20polls.%20But%20with%20time%2C%20unfulfilled%20promises%2C%20among%20them%20better%20air%20quality%2C%20started%20bothering%20Delhiites.%20The%20ruling%20AAP%20asserted%20that%20the%20BJP%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%20was%20creating%20roadblocks%20in%20its%20functioning.%20But%20ten%20years%20into%20AAP%20rule%2C%20voters%20saw%20such%20allegations%20as%20excuses.%20Against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20AAP's%20constant%20run-ins%20with%20the%20Centre%2C%20the%20BJP's%20'double%20engine'%20promise%20appealed%20to%20the%20masses%20and%20the%20results%20reflect%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Sheesh%20Mahal'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20election%2C%20the%20BJP's%20attack%20on%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20focused%20on%20'Sheesh%20Mahal'%20--%20a%20term%20used%20to%20refer%20to%20the%20renovated%20Chief%20Minister's%20residence%20when%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20was%20in%20office.%20What%20added%20ammo%20to%20the%20BJP's%20charge%20is%20a%20report%20Comptroller%20and%20Auditor%20General%20of%20India.%20The%20CAG%20probe%2C%20according%20to%20news%20reports%2C%20found%20that%20the%20preliminary%20estimate%20for%20the%20renovation%20was%20Rs%207.91%20crore.%20This%20went%20up%20to%208.62%20crore%20when%20work%20was%20awarded%20in%202020.%20But%20by%20the%20time%20the%20Public%20Works%20Department%20completed%20the%20job%20in%202022%2C%20the%20cost%20had%20jumped%20to%20Rs%2033.66%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20countered%20the%20'Sheesh%20Mahal'%20charge%20with%20the%20'Rajmahal'%20barb%2C%20accusing%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20of%20an%20opulent%20lifestyle%20and%20daring%20the%20BJP%20to%20show%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20residence.%20But%20the%20BJP's%20relentless%20campaign%20appears%20to%20have%20influenced%20voters%2C%20especially%20because%20it%20played%20out%20against%20AAP's%20promise%20of%20clean%20politics%20and%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20claims%20to%20remove%20VIP%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELiquor%20Policy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20government's%20current%20term%20witnessed%20a%20massive%20uproar%20over%20corruption%20allegations%20surrounding%20Delhi's%20now-scrapped%20liquor%20policy.%20The%20BJP%20accused%20the%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20government%20of%20%26quot%3Bturning%20Delhi%20into%20a%20city%20of%20drunkards%26quot%3B%20after%20the%20new%20policy%20brought%20'Buy%201%20Get%201%20free'%20offers%20on%20liquor%20bottles.%20The%20AAP%20consistently%20denied%20any%20allegation%20in%20the%20liquor%20policy%2C%20which%20was%20scrapped%20less%20than%20a%20year%20after%20it%20was%20improved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProbes%20by%20central%20agencies%20led%20to%20the%20arrest%20of%20top%20leaders%2C%20including%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20Manish%20Sisodia%20and%20Sanjay%20Singh.%20After%20Mr%20Sisodia%20was%20arrested%2C%20he%20stepped%20down%20as%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20AAP%20had%20to%20rejig%20its%20cabinet.%20Then%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20was%20arrested%20and%20remained%20in%20prison%20for%20five%20months.%20The%20arrests%20of%20multiple%20top%20leaders%20kept%20the%20AAP%20in%20firefighting%20mode%20throughout%20its%20third%20term%2C%20taking%20the%20focus%20away%20from%20fulfilling%20its%202020%20poll%20promises.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738993080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fdbhcfof_bjp-delhi_625x300_08_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-election-results-live-