20one%20of%20defendants'%20actions%20to%20dismantle%20USAID%20were%20taken%20pursuant%20to%20congressional%20authorization.%20And%20pursuant%20to%20federal%20statute%2C%20Congress%20is%20the%20only%20entity%20that%20may%20lawfully%20dismantle%20the%20agency%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20argued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20humanitarian%20aid%20agency%20has%20been%20under%20fire%20since%20Trump%20took%20office.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1886307316804263979%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EX%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Monday%20that%20he%20%26quot%3Bspent%20the%20weekend%20feeding%20USAID%20into%20the%20wood%20chipper.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20USAID%20said%20nearly%20all%20staff%20would%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fusaid-staff-put-on-administrative-leave-friday-midnight-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplaced%20on%20administrative%20leave%3C%2Fa%3E%20starting%20on%20February%207%20at%20midnight.%20The%20announcement%20came%20just%20a%20day%20after%20the%20agency%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fusaid-workers-stay-home-elon-musk-trump-shut-down-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshut%20down%20its%20headquarters%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Monday%20and%20told%20staff%20to%20work%20remotely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20regards%20to%20the%20USAID%20stuff%2C%20I%20went%20over%20it%20in%20detail%2C%20and%20he%20agreed%20that%20we%20should%20shut%20it%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said%20of%20a%20conversation%20he%20had%20with%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20during%20an%20X%20Spaces%20conversation%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEstablished%20in%201961%20by%20then-President%20John%20F.%20Kennedy%2C%20USAID%20oversees%20the%20US's%20aid%20programs%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20spent%20nearly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fforeignassistance.gov%2Fdata%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2432.5%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20fiscal%20year%202024%2C%20channeling%20aid%20to%20countries%20like%20Ukraine%2C%20Jordan%2C%20and%20Ethiopia.%20The%20US%20is%20the%20world's%20largest%20provider%20of%20humanitarian%20aid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20turmoil%20surrounding%20USAID%20occurs%20amid%20a%20wider%20upending%20of%20the%20federal%20bureaucracy%20during%20Trump's%20second%20term%2C%20with%20the%20federal%20judiciary%20increasingly%20stepping%20in.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ELast%20month%2C%20the%20Trump%20administration%20gave%20federal%20employees%20from%20January%2028%20to%20February%206%20to%20accept%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-federal-workers-employee-buyout-read-opm-letter-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuyout%20offer%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20resign%20from%20their%20jobs%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffederal-buyout-deferred-resignation-deadline-extended-trump-court-decision-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20judge%20extended%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20deadline%20to%20Monday.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20Trump%20administration's%20freeze%20on%20federal%20grants%20and%20loans%20was%20announced%20on%20January%2028%20and%20rolled%20by%20within%20days%2C%20with%20a%20federal%20judge%20issuing%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-musk-doge-timeline-federal-workforce-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erestraining%20order%20on%20January%2031.%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EA%20federal%20judge%20also%20issued%20an%20injunction%20against%20Trump's%20executive%20orders%20on%20ending%20birthright%20citizenship%2C%20calling%20them%20%26quot%3Bflatly%20unconstitutional.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Office%20of%20Personnel%20Management%2C%20which%20oversees%20the%20federal%20workforce%2C%20said%20on%20Thursday%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F40-000-federal-workers-buyout-trump-goal-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eover%2040%2C000%20employees%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20accepted%20the%20offer.%20The%20federal%20government%20employs%20more%20than%202%20million%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-musk-doge-usaid-shutdown-blocked-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738972209000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a67dd8eb4be2fff9a405a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-musk-doge-usaid-shutdown-blocked-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Judge%20Carl%20Nichols%20blocked%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20Elon%20Musk's%20attempted%20USAID%20shutdown%20days%20after%20the%20American%20Foreign%20Service%20Association%20filed%20a%20lawsuit.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktan%40businessinsider.com%20(Kwan%20Wei%20Kevin%20Tan%2CKelsey%20Vlamis%2CKatherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A444%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-musk-doge-usaid-shutdown-blocked-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Some%20American%20shoppers%20are%20getting%20asked%20to%20pay%20high%20fees%20to%20receive%20their%20packages%20after%20Trump's%20new%20China%20tariffs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227383%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Containers%20and%20vehicles%20with%20the%20DHL%20logo%20stand%20at%20the%20DHL%20parcel%20center.%20The%20connection%20to%20the%20existing%20parcel%20center%20creates%20the%20largest%20Deutsche%20Post%20DHL%20parcel%20processing%20site%20in%20Germany.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F642d1db7fcb86b00180334a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESome%20shoppers%20who%20placed%20orders%20through%20DHL%20Express%20said%20they%20were%20hit%20with%20high%20fees%2C%20sometimes%20more%20than%20the%20item's%20retail%20price%2C%20since%20Trump's%20China%20tariffs%20went%20into%20effect.%3Cp%3ESven%20Hoppe%2Fpicture%20alliance%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EUS%20shoppers%20said%20they've%20received%20higher%20shipping-related%20fees%20after%20Trump's%20new%20tariffs%20on%20Chinese%20goods%20went%20into%20effect.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETrump%20ordered%20the%20end%20of%20the%20de%20minimis%20exemption%2C%20long%20used%20by%20Shein%20and%20Temu%20to%20avoid%20import%20fees.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHowever%2C%20a%20follow-up%20executive%20order%20signed%20by%20Trump%20on%20Friday%20paused%20the%20ending%20of%20the%20de%20minimis%20exemption.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20pressed%20pause%20on%20an%20earlier%20executive%20order%20to%20end%20an%20exemption%20used%20by%20Chinese%20e-commerce%20giants%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshein-temu-de-minimis-tax-loophole-scrutiny-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShein%20and%20Temu%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20avoid%20import%20fees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20some%20Americans%20have%20received%20messages%20from%20companies%20and%20shipping%20firms%20this%20week%20asking%20them%20to%20pay%20additional%20fees%20in%20order%20to%20receive%20the%20packages%20they%20had%20previously%20ordered.%20Some%20of%20the%20shoppers%20shared%20screenshots%20of%20the%20messages%20and%20their%20purchase%20receipts%20with%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMelissa%20Covarrubias%2C%20a%20San%20Diego-based%20influencer%2C%20paid%20additional%20fees%20of%20over%20%24100%20on%20an%20order%20shipped%20through%20DHL.%20Covarrubias%20told%20BI%20the%20added%20costs%20felt%20like%20%26quot%3Banother%20way%20to%20squeeze%20more%20money%20from%20everyday%20consumers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Trump%20initially%20signed%20an%20executive%20order%20on%20Saturday%20to%20implement%20new%20tariffs%20on%20imported%20goods%20from%20China%2C%20Canada%2C%20and%20Mexico%20and%20ended%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbrands-scramble-as-trump-ends-de-minimis-shipments-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ede%20minimis%20exemption%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%20he%20later%20announced%20the%20tariffs%20on%20Canada%20and%20Mexico%20would%20be%20paused%20for%20a%20month%2C%20and%20on%20Friday%20issued%20a%20temporary%20pause%20on%20the%20removal%20of%20the%20de%20minimis%20exemption%20through%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fpresidential-actions%2F2025%2F02%2Famendment-to-duties-addressing-the-synthetic-opioid-supply-chain-in-the-peoples-republic-of-china%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanother%20executive%20order%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESection%20321%2C%20also%20known%20as%20de%20minimis%2C%20let%20importers%20avoid%20paying%20duty%20and%20tax%20on%20shipments%20valued%20under%20%24800%20that%20were%20headed%20directly%20to%20US%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20US%20consumers%20have%20taken%20to%20social%20media%20in%20the%20last%20week%20to%20share%20examples%20of%20being%20charged%20outstanding%20duty%20fees%20on%20imported%20orders%20from%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECovarrubias%20said%20she%20placed%20an%20order%20with%20Australian-based%20athleisure%20brand%20Crop%20Shop%20Boutique%20through%20DHL's%20delivery%20service%2C%20which%20initially%20cost%20%24305.%20She%20paid%20the%20original%20price%20for%20her%20order%20and%20was%20later%20asked%20to%20pay%20a%20%26quot%3Bduty%20payment%26quot%3B%20of%20%24115.91.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCSB%20assured%20customers%20that%20they%20would%20either%20cover%2050%25%20of%20the%20tariffs%20or%20provide%20a%20gift%20card%20for%20the%20same%20amount%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BSince%20my%20package%20had%20already%20arrived%20in%20San%20Diego%2C%20I%20paid%20the%20full%20tariff%20fee%20of%20%24115.91%2C%20and%20CSB%20later%20refunded%20me%20half.%20While%20I%20appreciate%20the%20partial%20reimbursement%2C%20the%20high%20duty%20fees%20make%20me%20hesitant%20to%20shop%20with%20them%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECSB's%20website%20says%20that%20its%20suppliers%20and%20manufacturers%20are%20located%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhelp.shopcsb.com%2Fen_us%2Fis-your-packaging-sustainable-and-recyclable-HybA4OM72%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAt%2520CSB%2520we%2520do%2520our%2Cwe%2520can%2520continue%2520to%2520improve.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChina%20and%20Turkey%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20that%20its%20shipments%20come%20from%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhelp.shopcsb.com%2Fen_us%2Fcategories%2Fdispatch-delivery-HJHJ8Jrx0%23%3A~%3Atext%3DWe%2520ship%2520all%2520orders%2520from%2520our%2520warehouse%2520based%2520in%2520Queensland%252C%2520Australia.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewarehouse%20in%20Queensland%2C%20Australia%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20spokesperson%20for%20CSB%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDHL%20Express%20has%20a%20standardized%20set%20of%20fees%20and%20handling%20charges%20that%20apply%20for%20the%20customs%20clearance%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20DHL%20spokesperson%20said.%20%26quot%3BThese%20fees%20are%20in%20addition%20to%20government%20taxes%20and%20duties.%20Charges%20vary%20by%20shipment%20and%20are%20listed%20on%20our%20website.%20Shipments%20under%20the%20de%20minimis%20threshold%20are%20exempt.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECristina%20Adams%2C%20a%20beauty%20and%20lifestyle%20influencer%2C%20said%20she%20had%20a%20similar%20experience%2C%20waiting%20on%20a%20pair%20of%20frames%20from%20Lensmart%20en%20route%20from%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdams%20said%20that%20after%20she%20paid%20for%20her%20order%20%E2%80%94%20%2414.95%20for%20the%20frames%20and%20an%20extra%20%2421.95%20for%20expedited%20shipping%20%E2%80%94%20she%20received%20an%20email%