8651480-800x600.jpeg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-02-04-at-11.11.51-1-1738651480-600x450.jpeg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-02-04-at-11.11.51-1-1738651480-400x300.jpeg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-02-04-at-11.11.51-1-1738651480-200x150.jpeg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-02-04-at-11.11.51-1-1738651480-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-403030%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHarteij%20stands%20as%20an%20inspiration%20for%20other%20cancer%20patients%20and%20teaches%20them%20to%20stay%20hopeful.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202014%2C%20I%20moved%20to%20Bengaluru%20to%20pursue%20my%20MBA.%20After%20getting%20another%20PET%20scan%2C%20I%20discovered%20the%20cancer%20had%20escalated%20to%20the%20fourth%20stage%20and%20had%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F371020%2Fblood-cancer-stem-cell-donors-dkms-bmst-foundation-india-leukaemia-saving-lives%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espread%20to%20my%20bone%20marrow%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20decided%20to%20switch%20to%20allopathic%20treatment.%20I%20moved%20to%20Hyderabad%20to%20stay%20with%20my%20brother%20and%20made%20the%20difficult%20choice%20to%20leave%20my%20MBA%20programme%20behind.%20The%20real%20treatment%20began%20in%20the%20final%20stage%20of%20cancer.%20I%20received%20my%20treatment%20at%20the%20Indo-American%20Cancer%20Institute%2C%20also%20known%20as%20Basavatarakam%20Cancer%20Hospital%2C%20under%20the%20care%20of%20Dr%20Senthil%20Rajappa%2C%E2%80%9D%20Harteij%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-sl